<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="11Mar1937"><font color="red">11 March 1937</font> <i>NLVP</i> (from Ben Huebsch to Paul L&eacute;on): I am glad to know that &ldquo;Work in Progress&rdquo; engages Mr Joyce&apos;s attention, and that you have the feeling that it will be ready by the Autumn. </div>
